{"tid":1848863,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"李桂華指反修例事件將有更多人被起訴　否認濫捕","createTime":"2020-01-28T16:49:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T17:14:56.000Z","uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"780ad70edc800666684b08c22872a73eac38fe44","tid":1848863,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T16:49:41.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】反修例風波以來，警方拘捕了七千多名與示威活動相關的人士，暫時只有約一成半人被起訴。有組織罪案及三合會調查科高級警司李桂華解釋，程序需時，並非濫捕，又形容被捕人士年紀越來越輕，作為執法者感到心痛。<br />\n<br />\n過去多個月的示威埸合，警民之間不時出現這樣情況。<br />\n<br />\n無論他們是路人、街坊還是示威者，有織罪案及三合會調查科高級警司李桂華說，根據警隊條例，只要警員合理地相信某人犯罪，已可作出拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n截至上周二，警方拘捕了7143人，當中只有1106人，即約一成半人被起訴。李桂華指並非濫捕。<br />\n<br />\n對於警員被指暴力對待羈留人士，李桂華反問作出指責的人為何往往蒙面或背着鏡頭。<br />\n<br />\n李桂華在警隊工作多年，過去面對的多是黑社會分子，作為執法者，他表示今次的感受不同。<br />\n<br />\n他曾接觸不少年青的被捕者，發現他們的動機是出於憤怒，認為這些憤怒與一連串的社會事件有關。他形容警方站在風眼最前線，明白為何會被針對。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=378423\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D378423&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGZriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=9d571730\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D378423&h=b3ee11fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=378423</a>"},{"pid":"564f42c13cba4d8047bbf8ce282bf3a26b4bfc18","tid":1848863,"uid":122275,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T16:59:44.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"d5f9fb25995fd6993768339c9d234f4f4a0bb6ce","tid":1848863,"uid":169074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T17:01:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"45d62de69e9411c09e95811b0ef045cca7dcd88e","tid":1848863,"uid":62815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T17:01:44.000Z","msg":"報應就到喇"},{"pid":"7ed896a4bfd5fc7e52172ecea7c334c7fde03825","tid":1848863,"uid":160592,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T17:04:47.000Z","msg":"黎緊陪審團好重要，中左唔好推呀"},{"pid":"47591460366eac6ef60558b3e6c8348fc834638a","tid":1848863,"uid":306664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T17:05:06.000Z","msg":"貓哭老鼠假慈悲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b167c8a618761a4a4b126f8e596ed0bf42d6a427","tid":1848863,"uid":109505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T17:07:57.000Z","msg":"捉六千個，要起訴幾多個先唔叫濫捕？"},{"pid":"f289f7b0054a8698f25b4f81fae697da64ef7924","tid":1848863,"uid":186181,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T17:09:20.000Z","msg":"句句都難聽過粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2732c734814c25f1144e078b2ab563e48cfac061","tid":1848863,"uid":168389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T17:11:25.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"5c19014c0337d3224848c6bc2d814246898d5baf","tid":1848863,"uid":189650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T17:12:38.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"41df37c8c848e736faec9b2807aca6db984dbed2","tid":1848863,"uid":134438,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T17:13:16.000Z","msg":"黑警唔死全家 浩園起嚟做咩？"},{"pid":"bdcc9545f91422eebd44005a666cb8a30930dab3","tid":1848863,"uid":48579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T17:13:56.000Z","msg":"你無九成都唔好話無濫捕"},{"pid":"22737383f48db191ec6733ba5195136cc7aa4195","tid":1848863,"uid":77937,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T17:14:45.000Z","msg":"李桂華反問作出指責的人為何往往蒙面或背着鏡頭：講緊班狗？"},{"pid":"1bae4035e53370e66a8da5528120f61ad492743c","tid":1848863,"uid":221171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T17:14:56.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"}]}